+must prove gate clean through data that tests can inspect.
+**Impact:** `claim-gate-loop` and wavegraph receipts/tests.
+**Code Refs:** `core/orchestration/src/proof/claim-gate-loop.ts`,
+`core/orchestration/src/proof/claim-gate-wavegraph-slice.ts`
