+
+**When:** T+9
+**Context:** The user asked whether the plan actually uses all laid-out model
+families and emphasized lots of Claude Bridge, top Chinese checks, xAI, and
+Google TUI. The injected runner seam existed, but provider-specific runner
+factories were still missing.
+**Decision:** Add named runner factories for Claude Bridge process execution,
+OpenRouter HTTP lanes, xAI/Grok HTTP lanes, Google Gemini TUI process
