+## Gate Ladder
+
+This is the implementation ladder, but it is not purely linear. Later gates can reopen earlier ones.
+
+### Gate 0: Patch Packet / Tick / Honesty Boundary
+
+Make the work enter Lev as a bounded Tick with a patch packet, source refs, declared claim ceiling, and receipt target.
+
+### Gate 0A: Model Lane Formation
+
+Before any council claims multi-model diversity, model lanes must be declared,
+data-export gated, and receipt-bearing.
