+# ClaimGate Wavegraph Slice Implementation Report - 2026-06-23
+
+## Scope
+
+Implemented the first executable slice for the ClaimGate cognitive wavegraph
+goal:
+
+```text
+Gate 0 / Gate 0A / Gate 1 / Gate 2 tiny slice
+  -> FlowMind / execution-contract shaped workflow spec
+  -> workflow topology receipt
+  -> model-lane manifests, receipts, and injected runner outcomes
+  -> cognitive member manifests
+  -> context load plan compiled into loaded skill/MMM/source receipts
+  -> nested two-wave fixture
+  -> management sidecars
+  -> management-plane actions and receipt
+  -> forced failure
+  -> FailurePacket
+  -> requeue
+  -> deterministic gate clean after repair
+  -> proposal-only receipt bundle
+```
+
