+  receipt-synthesis roles do not collapse into one Claude output. More Claude
+  Bridge lanes are allowed when each lane preserves its own receipt.
+- xAI/Grok lane receipt or availability receipt.
+- Google/Gemini TUI lane receipt or availability receipt. A generic Google
