+  Gemini TUI process invocation, and Codex/local deterministic checks. These
+  factories are dependency-injected and tested; they do not hardcode live auth,
+  network, or CLI execution into the proof core.
+- the runtime runner seam now independently blocks `private_approved` outside
+  providers without `dataExportApprovalRef`, so adapter execution cannot bypass
+  the slice-level data-export gate.
+
